00:12:03.792 --> 00:12:06.446
in the middle of the Pacific Ocean.

00:12:08.156 --> 00:12:11.696
This is the Jean-Marie Tjibaou Center.

00:12:11.720 --> 00:12:14.545
It's for the Kanaky ethnic group.

